OL,3,CMidwife whistleblower calls for change
OL,4,Cdue to 'crisis' in maternity care
OL,6,F"Every night before a shift, it's
OL,7,Fanxiety, it's feeling sick," the
OL,8,Fmidwife, who asked to be anonymous,
OL,9,Ftold ITV News Central.
OL,11,F"You start the shift anxious because
OL,12,Fyou don't know what's going to come
OL,13,Fthrough the door and you leave the
OL,14,Fshift thinking that you've not done
OL,15,Fgood enough."
OL,17,FThe midwife said there are also
OL,18,Fserious safety problems across wards,
OL,19,Fwith maternity units overstretched and
OL,20,Funderstaffed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
