OL,3,CMidwife whistleblower calls for change
OL,4,Cdue to 'crisis' in maternity care
OL,6,F"I look at the staffing and I look at
OL,7,Fthe equipment we have available and I
OL,8,Fjust think, how are we going to
OL,9,Fmaintain safety today?
OL,11,F"You pull the emergency bell and you
OL,12,Fthink for a second 'is somebody going
OL,13,Fto come or am I it?'"
OL,15,F"There have been times where I've sat
OL,16,Fin a room with a woman that needs a
OL,17,Fbaby delivered, and it's just a
OL,18,Fticking time bomb. But we can't
OL,19,Fphysically do anything because there
OL,20,Fare no theatres."
