OL,3,CMidwife whistleblower calls for change
OL,4,Cdue to 'crisis' in maternity care
OL,6,FIn recent years, midwives have raised
OL,7,Fsimilar concerns over working
OL,8,Fconditions.
OL,10,FThe CQC has launched a national
OL,11,Fmaternity inspection programme into
OL,12,Fall of England's maternity units to
OL,13,Fgive the fullest picture of what care
OL,14,Flooks like right now.
OL,16,FThis midwife doesn't believe any
OL,17,Finvestigation will show the true
OL,18,Fextent of failings.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
