OL,3,CMidwife whistleblower calls for change
OL,4,Cdue to 'crisis' in maternity care
OL,6,F"We are almost prepped for when the
OL,7,FCQC is coming, you see a lot more
OL,8,Fmanagement present that you probably
OL,9,Fwouldn't see, and there's a lot more
OL,10,Fstaff put on. There's people
OL,11,Fcompleting clinical checks, that
OL,12,Fwouldn't normally do to make it look
OL,13,Flike that's being done."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
