OL,3,CMidwife whistleblower calls for change
OL,4,Cdue to 'crisis' in maternity care
OL,6,F"To then see this almost circus show
OL,7,Fgoing on, it is quite angering, to be
OL,8,Fhonest. This is not the reality of
OL,9,Fwhat we're working in. You are not
OL,10,Fgoing to get the support and the
OL,11,Fbudgets, unless they see it in the
OL,12,Fabsolute dregs that it is on a day to
OL,13,Fday basis."
OL,15,FWhen asked if there was a crisis in
OL,16,Fmaternity care, the midwife replied
OL,17,Fwithout hesitation: "Yes, absolutely."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
