OL,3,CMidwife whistleblower calls for change
OL,4,Cdue to 'crisis' in maternity care
OL,6,F"I think that the more that it is
OL,7,Foverlooked and not placed as a
OL,8,Fpriority, the impact will be poorer
OL,9,Foutcomes. I think the more that we
OL,10,Fignore it, the more that the care
OL,11,Fbecomes unsafe over time because the
OL,12,Fstaffing is the worst I've ever seen.
OL,14,F"If you don't think there's a crisis
OL,15,Fas government or clinical directors of
OL,16,Fhospitals, then you're delusional.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
