OL,3,CMidwife whistleblower calls for change
OL,4,Cdue to 'crisis' in maternity care
OL,6,F"The Government has to listen to those
OL,7,Fstaff and women who are working in and
OL,8,Fusing our maternity services and it
OL,9,Fhas to act.
OL,11,F"We have had review after review
OL,12,Flaying out the same conclusions and
OL,13,Frecommendations, yet still the
OL,14,FGovernment shows no urgency. Maternity
OL,15,Fstaff and the women and families in
OL,16,Ftheir care deserve better."
