OL,6,FITV News Central asked the CQC about
OL,7,Fthe midwife's allegations. They said
OL,8,Fthat on some inspections, trusts are
OL,9,Fgiven 48 hours' notice, but most risk-
OL,10,Fbased inspections are unannounced.
OL,11,FThey also said they "use a wide range
OL,12,Fof data and intelligence to monitor
OL,13,Fthe quality and safety of services
OL,14,Fbeing provided".
