OL,6,FA spokesperson from the Department of
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care said: "We are
OL,8,Fcommitted to ensuring all women
OL,9,Freceive safe and compassionate care
OL,10,Ffrom maternity services and this is a
OL,11,Fpriority in our Women's Health
OL,12,FStrategy for 2024.
OL,14,F"NHS England's three-year plan for
OL,15,Fmaternity and neonatal services,
OL,16,Fbacked by #186 million per year from
OL,17,FApril, will make maternity services
OL,18,Fsafer, more personalised, and more
OL,19,Fequitable for women, babies, and
OL,20,Ffamilies."
